HEADWORD: Wielder
<hw>Wield"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who wields or
employs; a manager; a controller.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A <qex>wielder</qex> of the great arm of the war.</q>
